      <section class="section compact">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>For EV drivers who want to leave home with fewer unknowns.</h2>
            <p class="lead">
              VeVolt brings together what matters for charging: nearby stations,
              range, estimated cost, connector types and monthly savings.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="audience">
            <article class="audience-block">
              <h3>Electric and plug-in hybrid vehicles</h3>
              <p>
                Choose where to charge, when to stop and what charging means for
                the real cost of your trip.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="audience-block">
              <h3>From city driving to trip planning</h3>
              <p>
                Review your options before you leave or while travelling and
                take uncertainty out of charging.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="features" class="section band">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>
              Everything you need to plan a charge, without the complexity.
            </h2>
            <p class="lead">
              Tools focused on the driver's decisions: find stations, estimate a
              route, understand costs and keep vehicle details close at hand.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-grid">
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">01</div>
              <h3>Charger map</h3>
              <p>See nearby charging locations, distance, availability and connectors in one clear map.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">02</div>
              <h3>Station details</h3>
              <p>Check status, power, connector and reported price before opening directions or saving a location.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">03</div>
              <h3>Route and range</h3>
              <p>Compare distance, current battery and estimated range on arrival before opening navigation.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">04</div>
              <h3>QR code scanner</h3>
              <p>Scan a charging point QR code to record the session directly on your device.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">05</div>
              <h3>Visible savings</h3>
              <p>Track recorded energy, charging cost and sessions to understand your EV savings.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">06</div>
              <h3>VeVolt Market</h3>
              <p>Find nearby stores, dealerships and repair shops with directions and service filters.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">07</div>
              <h3>Vehicle profile</h3>
              <p>Add type, brand, model, battery, range and connector to personalize your estimates.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">08</div>
              <h3>VeVolt Community</h3>
              <p>Share status, price, a rating, comment or photo and follow reports from other EV drivers.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">09</div>
              <h3>VeVolt Condo</h3>
              <p>Organize invitations, reservations and sessions for shared private condominium chargers.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature">
              <div class="feature-code">10</div>
              <h3>Premium and local data</h3>
              <p>Unlock detailed history, a five-vehicle garage, CSV export, recommendations, alerts and Condo administration.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
