          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>Clear privacy, so you can use VeVolt with confidence.</h2>
            <p class="lead">
              VeVolt is designed to provide useful information through clear,
              purpose-specific permissions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-grid">
            <article class="trust-item">
              <h3>Personal data stays on-device</h3>
              <p>Vehicle details, saved locations and personal history remain in Android private storage.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="trust-item">
              <h3>Permissions under your control</h3>
              <p>
                Location and camera access are used only for map, route and QR
                Code features.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="trust-item">
              <h3>Google Play payments</h3>
              <p>
                Premium features are processed securely through your Google Play
                account.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="trust-item">
              <h3>Community controls</h3>
              <p>
                Reports can be flagged, blocked and deleted by their author;
                photos are processed to strip metadata.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
